cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.CR

The paper deals with person recognition using computer vision techniques, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed approach involves training multiple models for specific poses, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a new network architecture for learning person representations, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper introduces new benchmarks for evaluating person recognition, which involves security and cryptography (cs.CR).
